  check if is_koutput, bug #59159

  02 Aug 2004; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> lirc-0.7.0_pre7.ebuild:
  add lircmd init script, bug #17167

*lirc-0.7.0_pre7 (02 Aug 2004)

